# Climate Scope Insight – Infosys Springboard Internship

## Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing climate-related data to gain insights about environmental patterns and sustainability indicators.

## Objectives
- Perform data cleaning and preprocessing
- Conduct exploratory data analysis (EDA)
- Identify key insights and patterns
- Visualize results using Python libraries (Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly)
- Generate a final report with conclusions

## Files Included
- `dataset.csv` – Raw dataset used for analysis  
- `analysis.ipynb` – Jupyter Notebook with code and visualizations  
- `report.pdf` – Final project report summarizing the findings  

